      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00004",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "忆昔当年起战场，如今垂念汉高皇。绪成岁战未浆琼，投笔封侯日如朗。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00005",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "本爵定远侯班超，在汉皇驾前为臣。奉主旨意，去往西凉各国催贡。为此带领人马前往。众将官。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00006",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八龙套",
        "四大将"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00007",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "人马可齐？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00008",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四大将"
      ],
      "text": "俱已齐备。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00009",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "如此带马伺候。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00010",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
