      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮正板",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "叹不尽功名事古今贤良。在金殿领王命镇守西凉，惟愿得西番地复归我皇。玉门关观杀得风吹草芒，亦似有渔樵人放牛牧羊。看将来西番地原非草莽，但愿得此一去复归我邦。",
      "text_length": 77
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00012",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00013",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、四番将、匈奴王上。〖急急风〗。〖点绛唇〗。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00014",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "某，匈奴国王达里呵，适才探马报道，班超前来催贡。何不乘此机会，以下反上，岂不是好。众巴图鲁。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00015",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四龙套",
        "四番将"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00016",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "带马。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00017",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00018",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套同上，同站门。鄯善王上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00019",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "眼观旌旗起，耳听好消息。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00020",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00021",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "定远侯驾到。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00022",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "有请。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00023",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超上。报子下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00024",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "吓。侯爷。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00025",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "老大王。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00026",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "请坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00027",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "谢坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00028",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "不知侯爷驾到，未曾远迎，多有得罪。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00029",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。末将来的鲁莽，老大王海涵。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00030",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "侯爷到此何事？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00031",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "奉了汉天子之命，相邀老大王，年年进贡，每岁来朝。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00032",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "情愿年年进贡，每岁来朝。请至馆驿。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00033",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "告辞了。带马。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00034",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超下。报子上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00035",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "匈奴国王驾到。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00036",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "有请。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00037",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "匈奴王上。报子下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00038",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "王兄。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00039",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "御弟请坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00040",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "告坐。适才何人到此？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00041",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "班侯爷到来，催讨贡俸。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00042",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "老大王怎样回答？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00043",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "情愿年年进贡，每岁来朝。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00044",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "此人现在何处？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00045",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "现在馆驿。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00046",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "小弟有计在此。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00047",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "有何妙计？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00048",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "今晚三更时分，将馆驿团团围住，将班超杀死，以免我等数载贡俸。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00049",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "此计甚好。御弟前行，孤家大兵，随后接应。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00050",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "众将官，抬枪带马。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00051",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00052",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超上。四大将同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00053",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "想高皇坐江山全亏韩信，吕太后与萧何害却忠臣。斩英布诛彭越三杰丧命，已有那张子房告老归林。数百年至平帝王莽乱政，天不灭汉家后光武中兴。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00054",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "列位将军，桌案现有酒宴，大家畅饮一回。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00055",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四大将"
      ],
      "text": "侯爷请。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00056",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "列位将军。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00057",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00058",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "呀呀呀。你我安息了吧。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00059",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超睡。阴锣。虎形上，站班超后。四大将同醒，同看。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00060",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四大将"
      ],
      "text": "侯爷醒来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00061",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00062",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "耳边厢忽听得有人喧嚷。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00063",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超醒，看。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00064",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "又只见众将军站立两旁。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00065",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "列位将军，何事惊慌？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00066",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四大将"
      ],
      "text": "启侯爷：猛虎出现。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00067",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00068",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，猛虎出现，乃大吉之兆。有道是“不入虎穴，焉得虎子”。呀！",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00069",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "交锋之际加兵将，大小儿郎要提防。你我暂且把马上，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00070",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四大将同下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00071",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "惟愿此阵收复西凉。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00072",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超上马，下。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00073",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "匈奴王上，四番将、四龙套同上。〖急急风〗。众人过场同下。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00074",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超、四大将同上。〖急急风〗。会阵。四番将、匈奴王同上。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00075",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "马前敢是达里呵？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00076",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "然。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00077",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "带领人马前来则甚？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00078",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "匈奴王"
      ],
      "text": "住了。想我西凉各国，哪有贡献与你！特地前来，与你见个高下。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00079",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "好反复无常的匹夫，放马过来！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00080",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "班超、匈奴王同开打，同下，同上。匈奴王接，四大将同下。班超杀匈奴王下。鄯善王上，跪。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00081",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "老大王，还有何话讲？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00082",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鄯善王"
      ],
      "text": "情愿年年进贡，岁岁来朝。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00083",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "鄯善王下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00084",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "众将官，回朝缴旨。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00085",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖尾声〗。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00086",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "班超"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013015_e00087",
      "play_id": "01013015",
      "scene_id": "01013015_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
